01:01.320 --> 01:05.980
game about privacy, as they realized that after several global scandals, people feel

01:05.980 --> 01:07.840
increasingly vulnerable.

01:07.840 --> 01:11.960
They continue, it's unfortunate that this shift had to happen in order for tech companies

01:11.960 --> 01:13.140
to take notice.

01:13.140 --> 01:15.740
