02:47.320 --> 02:52.720
services together, privacy tracking, the Facebook container, the monitoring service and they're

02:52.720 --> 02:56.360
saying this is Firefox.

02:56.360 --> 02:58.880
I really like this.

02:58.880 --> 03:00.340
I think this is super important.

03:00.340 --> 03:03.320
